OL,3,CInquest to open into death of boxing
OL,4,Clegend Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of former
OL,7,Fworld boxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,8,Fwill be held.
OL,10,FThe hearing at Stockport Coroner's
OL,11,FCourt on 20 March follows the sudden
OL,12,Fpassing of the 46-year-old, whose
OL,13,Fdeath left the sporting world in shock.
OL,15,FA pre-inquest hearing previously heard
OL,16,Fthat the former boxer, known to fans
OL,17,Fas "The Hitman", was last seen by his
OL,18,Ffamily on 12 September, appearing to
OL,19,Fbe "well."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
