PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774019480
OL,3,CInquest to open into death of boxing
OL,4,Clegend Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FBut concerns were raised the following
OL,7,Fday when he failed to attend a
OL,8,Fscheduled event.
OL,10,FOn Sunday, 14 September 2025, his
OL,11,Fmanager, Paul Speak, arrived at
OL,12,FHatton's home in Hyde, Tameside, to
OL,13,Fcollect him for a flight to Dubai. He
OL,14,Ffound the former champion unresponsive.
OL,16,FThe proud Mancunian and lifelong
OL,17,FManchester City fan was one of the
OL,18,Fmost beloved figures in British sport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
