PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774019480
OL,3,CInquest to open into death of boxing
OL,4,Clegend Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FHatton earned the title of "The
OL,7,FPeople's Champion," drawing tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of fans to Las Vegas during
OL,9,Fthe height of his career.
OL,11,FDespite his success, Hatton was
OL,12,Ffamously candid about his battles
OL,13,Foutside the ring, speaking candidly
OL,14,Fabout his struggles with mental health
OL,15,Fand issues with drink and drugs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
