FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774019480
OL,3,CInquest to open into death of boxing
OL,4,Clegend Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FAt the time of his death, his family
OL,7,Finsisted he was "in a good place" and
OL,8,Fwas looking forward to the future,
OL,9,Fwith his bags already packed for a
OL,10,Fplanned comeback fight in Dubai this
OL,11,FDecember.
OL,13,FThousands of fans lined the streets of
OL,14,FManchester for his funeral at the
OL,15,FCathedral in October 2025.
OL,17,FThe service was attended by icons of
OL,18,Fsport and music, including Liam
OL,19,FGallagher, Wayne Rooney, and Tyson
OL,20,FFury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
